	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What's the best way to constantly force the triangle and noise to output at the reduced level you get when using DCM?
<br />
<br />I'm thinking it would be better for balancing channels if those two channels were always output as if you were playing DCM, even when you're not.

		

